    "description": "<strong>Super Hoopers is a basketball-themed game featuring three playable characters where their purpose is to carefully aim and throw the ball in order to score awesome basketball throws and trick shots. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/b80578634e51cb7476882a296f525b8c.webp?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/e9e18ca683973c7f0386aec34eb5d072.avif?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br>Set your aim ready into target and score in every way possible, lucky bouncy shots? no problem, find your own way to throw that ball into the hoop!<br>Make use of springs, force pads, walls or floor, anything counts!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/72385e5851ff09c869493b86187d0b84.webp?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/4381aa60262acb5fc93e2630b5e14a6f.avif?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br>Watch out for the obstacles and enemies that might interfere in your way.<br>Some red malicious mannequins are out everywhere keeping you from scoring, settings traps in order to make you fail, will you be able to beat them?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/84ead05236fc876c1f2f527243d9a6c1.webp?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/910b2ce93203da94ff5fef72eac8ea00.avif?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br>Three awesome characters: Cameron, Ryan and Rachel are waiting for you! each with their own themed-scenarios and a sweet short ending sequence.<br>Choose between journeys and discover each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240410/extras/aab11a6155b8e509ef96072ac48cb344.webp?t=1675344950\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br>There's an object to collect in every level, it can be a star, a key or a heart, depending on the character, will you be able to collect the item in every level?",
